{
  "stem": "7739.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you could only do this in the summertime.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You couldn't do it in the winter time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There used to be selections in the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Occasionally, they would come first thing in the morning, while the people were coming home from the night shift, and look us over after making a roll call.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And take out the weak ones, put them on a truck, take them to the next ravine or whatever, and then they shoot them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they used to bring back, occasionally-- they used to bring people from other locations where they were no longer needed, and to replace these workers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] If you were sick, there was a-- there was a barrack for a hospital.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was a one-way street.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You go in there, and you come out like a bag of bones.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They hardly feed you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The people were begging to be shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know what kind of [INAUDIBLE] there was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were shooting people for no reason.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And these people they didn't shoot, because they were sick.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The doctor attended them, but what could he do for them with no medicine?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Occasionally, when some people were being accused of doing sabotage in the factory, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] or if somebody ran away, they would-- they would have reprisals.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most of the time, if you were accused of doing sabotage in the factory, you either sabotaged the machinery or you sabotaged the product, they would shoot you right at the station.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Sometimes, they would find out later who did it, or who they suspected.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
